If your standee looks scratched and cloudy, don't worry, that's just the protective film doing its job! To remove the film, start at a corner and pick at the edge of the film with your fingernail (don't use anything sharp or it may scratch the acrylic underneath) and peel back from all sides, including the base. Crystal clear and beautiful! ☺️💜

🖤AgustD Trio🖤
Design drop 1/3!! 

To celebrate the upcoming tour and Yoongi’s history as AgustD, I have THREE AgustD pins in the works, one from each mixtape/album!

Going back to the beginning for this one, it’s 2016 AgustD spitting fire! 🔥🔥🔥

🖤AgustD Trio🖤
Design drop 2/3!! 

To celebrate the upcoming tour and Yoongi’s history as AgustD, here is the second pin in the trio, D-2!! Yoongi’s Daechwita looks are iconic, so of course that was my pick for this design!

Also, I changed my mind about putting the “tour” text on all 3 pins, so they now have the release year of their corresponding album (2016 for the OG mixtape, 2020 for D-2, 2023 for D-Day) instead. Swipe to see the modified version of the 2016 pin!

🖤AgustD Trio🖤
Design drop 3/3!! Ordering info will be coming soon!

To celebrate the upcoming tour and Yoongi’s history as AgustD, here is the final pin in the trio, based on the newly released People Pt.2! 

So this design sat half finished for a while before the song came out, and I had absolutely no idea what to expect for the aesthetic, just hoping and praying it would be something that fit well with the two pins I’d already designed. People Pt.2 doesn’t have a strong iconic look the way Daechwita and the first AgustD MVs do, but you know what? I think that fits. This gentler domestic version of AgustD feels like the end of a story that began loudly, full of anger, and now concludes with quiet confidence and introspection. I hope this story of the artist’s growth will come across when you see all three of these designs together. ❤️

🖤AgustD Tour Pin🖤
PREORDER IS CLOSED

Did you think I was done with AgustD pins? Never enough for Yoongi! 🥹 Here's one more design drop, a tour pin in honor of Yoongi's first solo tour! Whether you're lucky enough to be attending or will be watching from afar,  we're all so proud of his accomplishments. This commemorative pin is shiny hard enamel with silver plating, black rainbow glitter enamel, and a hanging charm. A list of the cities on the tour is engraved on the back of the pin!

AND, this pin will be a ✨FREEBIE✨ when you preorder the AgustD pin trio!! More Yoongi? More Yoongi. 😘 It will also be available for purchase separately if you just want one for yourself/your concert buddy.

🖤AgustD Pin Trio🖤

Celebrate 3 eras of AgustD, from 2016-2023!! Yoongi has had so much growth as an artist and a person over these years, healing from pain and anger to become the quietly confident person he is today, which is reflected in all of his music but especially his solo work. I find Yoongi's story to be so inspiring and can't wait to see what's next for him, D-Day and many years into the future. Fan for life! 🥹

💜 BTS x ARMY Anniversary Pin 💜
10th ANNIVERSARY EDITION 
**Available now on aptyaki.com**

This is a special rose-gold variant of the anniversary pin made by @greeneyedblackwolf and me last year! 

The design features the BTS (6/13) and ARMY (7/9) anniversary dates, smeraldo flowers, and cutout/engraved filigree areas. The logo in the center is a polished finish, so when you look at it, you'll see ARMY (yourself!) reflected in the heart of the pin. 💜 In addition to the plating color change, this version has more glitter sections for extra sparkle, and engraved on the back is "apobangpo" (ARMY forever, BTS forever) and "10 years together"!!

If you're local, you can get one of these babies at the @btsarmyegers cupsleeve event on June 11 (see my pinned post)! If not, I will have some available in my online shop 1-2 days after that!

💜Army bomb galaxy pin sets💜
Surprise unboxing... watch until the end for a bonus surprise!
 
Use these tiny pins to fill those small gaps on your pin board, or wear them in a little group on your clothing for maximum borahae energy. 😘 These will be available at the @btsarmyegers cupsleeve event on June 11, and online in my next shop update as in-stocks. More info to come!

💜 ArmyBomb Galaxy Mini Pin Set 💙
**Available now on aptyaki.com**

Surprise pin drop!!! All my previous tiny pins have been well loved, so I decided to make another set in honor of BTS's 10th anniversary and upcoming FESTA!

- Choice of blue set or purple set
- Each pin is approx 0.75-inch
- Soft enamel with epoxy topcoat
- Glow-in-the-dark enamel
- Glitter sections

I love tiny pins for pin boards because they're perfect for filling those small spaces between larger pins, but honestly, these looked so adorable on my jacket when I took the photos that I might leave one set on there forever... 😅💜

I'll have these at the @btsarmyegers cupsleeve event on June 11, along with the 10th anniversary BTS/ARMY pin. They will also be available as in-stocks on aptyaki.com during the next update, probably sometime in the next 2 weeks!

Let me know what you think of these!! 💜

💜FESTA 2023💜
Happy 10th anniversary to the boys and happy Festa to all of us!!! Dreaming of the day that all 7 are back together again. Until then... I'll just draw them together. 🥰

I owe BTS for a lot more than just their music and positive messages - through them I've met wonderful friends, found boundless inspiration, and gained the confidence to take some major steps toward my own happiness. People say "in this bangtan shit for life" and that's me as well. I'll never forget all the good things that loving them brought into my life. 

APOBANGPO! 💜

🌱 Letter 🌾
This month is my 4th anniversary as an ARMY artist!! The first thing I ever posted here was Jimin art, so my tradition is to do a new one every year. (Swipe to see the previous ones!)

I picked Letter for this year’s art. This performance took my breath away so I had to try and capture it. Perfect mood and setting for a beautiful song. Jimin’s vocals are nothing short of angelic, especially paired with the single guitar that lets them shine. I keep listening to it again and again 💜

This performance made me think of that old video of baby Jimin, wishing to have a voice that touches and moves people someday… I hope he sees this and all his work as proof of how he’s made his wish come true over the years. He is a magnificent singer and the whole Face album showcases that to perfection. Hard work always pays off!

Unboxed the whole set of AgustD pins and restocks of the tiny bag pins today!! 🥳 The box got stuck in transit for a long time so I was pretty anxious about it, but they're finally all here, safe and sound. I'm so pleased with the details, especially Yoongi's different facial expressions. They came out beautifully!!

I have a couple days of grading ahead, then I'll ship out the preorders. In-stocks will be going into my shop on July 9 (more info to come soon)!

Eras of AgustD - 2016

Pin 1/4 in the collection is Yoongi's iconic blond look from 2016! When I think of AgustD, it's the first thing that comes into my head, so I'm very happy to have been able to make a pin for this era.

In-stock pins will be available in my next update, on July 9!!

Eras of AgustD - 2020

Pin 2/4 in the collection is Daechwita from 2020! Remember when we all collectively lost our minds over the Daechwita mv?? It was a new side of Yoongi we'd never seen before and honestly I never recovered... did you? 😂 D-2 is my favorite Yoongi album.

In-stock pins will be available in my next update, on July 9!!

Eras of AgustD - 2023 (Haegeum version)

Pin 3/4 in the collection is Haegeum! I ended up doing two pins for this era, a hard version (Haegeum) and a soft version (People Pt.2). I love how D-Day gave us both sides of Yoongi, so I couldn't pick just one of them!!

In-stock pins will be available in my next update, on July 9!!

Eras of AgustD - 2023 (People version)

The 4th and last pin in the collection is People! Both People pt.1 & pt.2 showcase the softer parts of Yoongi, and I love that. Getting to hear Yoongi's gentle singing voice was a rare treat at the time when D-2 came out, and now 3 years later, we've got an entire tour of him belting his heart out on stage. Looking back on these previous iterations of AgustD really shows how far he's come, and I'm happy to be able to represent that with my art. 

In-stock pins will be available in my next update, on July 9!!

🖤AgustD Tour Pin🖤
Yoongi's silhouette filled with black rainbow glitter, like a sea of sparkling army bombs!! I hope you'll love this memento of Yoongi's first solo tour, and it will bring to mind lots of awesome concert memories whenever you look at it. 🥹

This pin will be available in my next update on July 9 (army day)!!

✨Pearl-finish Prints ✨
Going up in the shop on Friday Oct 6!

The video doesn't capture the effect that well, but I've been experimenting with different paper finishes for my prints. This one is "metallic satin", a pearl finish with subtle metallic shimmer throughout. It's incredibly pretty in person. It seems to work best with artwork that has a lot of white because the shimmer disappears under dark colors, so this option will only ever be available on a select few prints... not the kind of finish that suits everything. I'll keep playing with it some more!
